      <title>据称，在贝恩公司有意的情况下，Mobvista 正考虑出售 Mintegral 子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/mobvista-is-said-to-weigh-mintegral-unit-sale-amid-bain-interest</link>
